Package com.invensense.cubequat

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cube
    This class is the model class to for the rolling dice view to provide the abstract data that is necessary to setup and display the cube
    CubeView
    CubeView is the class that extend GLSurfaceView and it will acts as a View class to display a rolling dice cube on the application.
    Global
    This is a Global class that is primarily intended to provide a bridge between the sensor values that are shared between different classes and activities.
    OpenGLRenderer
    This class is responsible for rendering a CubeView over GLSurfaceView.
